window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>2044. The world of games changed long ago.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>\"Ascension\" has become one of the most popular VRMMO games. It is a huge world divided into a hundred Floors, with each Floor a boundless location with its own countries, tribes, and millions of players.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>The object of the game is to unlock all the gates and conquer the top.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Having joined the game, Will Thomson doesn't realize that he is all by himself. Then he accepts the first quest....</p> <p>Cursed Rat: level 46....</p>"; 
